<guid isPermaLink="false">12f124babf221f68c7753628676431b9</guid>
<description><![CDATA[<p>
*Californians are turning to vending machines for safer water. <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2019/dec/02/california-water-vending-machines-quality">Are they being
swindled</a>?*

<p>
